tests.name: File To TCP
tests.description:
This test measures the performance of the subject's ability to tail data from local
files and send it over TCP.

tests.name: Regex Parsing
tests.description:
This test measures the performance of the subject's ability parse strings with Regex
and place the extracted values in named keys.

tests.name: TCP To Blackhole
tests.description:
This test measures the raw internal performance of the subject by configuring it to
simply discard incoming data. Most subject include a "blackhole" or "null" output
for this purposes.

tests.name: TCP To HTTP
tests.description: This test measures the HTTP output performance for each subject.

tests.name: TCP To TCP
tests.description: This test measures the TCP output performance for each subject.
